description: The problem is an ImportError caused by the setdefault function not being able to find the desired module. When the program tries to import a module by using the setdefault function, the function returns an empty string instead of the module name, resulting in an ImportError.
code:
#Create an empty dictionary
dictionary = {}

#Set a default value for the dictionary
dictionary.setdefault('default', 0)

#Print the dictionary
print(dictionary)
